(165, 'slang', 17, 'What does \"Pick me\" mean in slang?', 'Someone desperate for attention or approval', 'Fashion brand', 'Funny joke', 'Smart choice', 'A', 30, 'pick_me.png', 'English: \"Pick me\" means someone trying hard to be liked.\nIndo: \"Pick me\" artinya orang yang cari perhatian agar dipilih atau disukai.'),
(166, 'slang', 17, 'What does \"Delulu\" mean in slang?', 'Delusional or imagining things', 'Cute and calm', 'Loud and rude', 'Always sleepy', 'A', 30, 'delulu.png', 'English: \"Delulu\" means being delusional or overly hopeful.\nIndo: \"Delulu\" artinya berhalusinasi atau berharap terlalu tinggi.'),
(167, 'slang', 17, 'What does \"Glow down\" mean in slang?', 'Looking worse than before', 'Brightening skin', 'Becoming famous', 'Trying new styles', 'A', 30, 'glow_down.png', 'English: \"Glow down\" means someone’s appearance got worse.\nIndo: \"Glow down\" artinya perubahan penampilan ke arah yang lebih buruk.'),
(168, 'slang', 17, 'What does \"Ick\" mean in slang?', 'Something that gives the ick or turns you off', 'Nice surprise', 'Cool outfit', 'Spicy food', 'A', 30, 'ick.png', 'English: \"Ick\" means something that gives you a sudden turn-off.\nIndo: \"Ick\" artinya hal kecil yang bikin langsung ilfeel.'),
(169, 'slang', 17, 'What does \"Slaps hard\" mean in slang?', 'Very good or impressive', 'Hurts badly', 'Too loud', 'Fast beat', 'A', 30, 'slaps_hard.png', 'English: \"Slaps hard\" means something is extremely good (like music).\nIndo: \"Slaps hard\" artinya sangat keren, terutama untuk lagu atau video.'),
(170, 'slang', 17, 'What does \"It’s the ___ for me\" mean in slang?', 'Highlighting a trait (often teasing)', 'Describing a job', 'Calling out names', 'Buying a gift', 'A', 30, 'its_the___for_me.png', 'English: \"It’s the ___ for me\" is used to point out something specific.\nIndo: \"It’s the ___ for me\" artinya menyoroti satu hal, biasanya sambil bercanda.'),
(171, 'slang', 18, 'What does \"A whole meal\" mean in slang?', 'Very attractive', 'Really hungry', 'Someone who cooks', 'Eating a lot', 'A', 30, 'a_whole_meal.png', 'English: \"A whole meal\" means someone looks extremely attractive.\nIndo: \"A whole meal\" artinya sangat menarik secara fisik.'),
(172, 'slang', 18, 'What does \"Bread\" mean in slang?', 'Money', 'Food', 'Joke', 'Shoes', 'A', 30, 'bread.png', 'English: \"Bread\" means money or income.\nIndo: \"Bread\" artinya uang atau penghasilan.'),
(173, 'slang', 18, 'What does \"CEO of ___\" mean in slang?', 'Expert or best at something', 'Office manager', 'Social media title', 'Real company boss', 'A', 30, 'ceo_of.png', 'English: \"CEO of ___\" means someone is very good at that thing.\nIndo: \"CEO of ___\" artinya sangat ahli dalam hal tertentu.'),
(174, 'slang', 18, 'What does \"Glow check\" mean in slang?', 'Before-after transformation comparison', 'Checking makeup', 'Sunlight test', 'Skin routine test', 'A', 30, 'glow_check.png', 'English: \"Glow check\" means showing before-and-after glow-up.\nIndo: \"Glow check\" artinya membandingkan perubahan penampilan sebelum dan sesudah.'),
(175, 'slang', 18, 'What does \"Dead inside\" mean in slang?', 'Emotionally drained or numb', 'Hungry', 'Overly happy', 'Sleeping too much', 'A', 30, 'dead_inside.png', 'English: \"Dead inside\" means feeling emotionally empty.\nIndo: \"Dead inside\" artinya merasa hampa atau lelah secara emosional.'),
(176, 'slang', 18, 'What does \"Caught in 4K\" mean in slang?', 'Clearly caught doing something', 'Filmed a movie', 'Bought a 4K TV', 'Looking great on camera', 'A', 30, 'caught_in_4k.png', 'English: \"Caught in 4K\" means getting caught clearly, usually in video.\nIndo: \"Caught in 4K\" artinya tertangkap basah dengan bukti yang jelas.'),
(177, 'slang', 18, 'What does \"Main character syndrome\" mean?', 'Acting overly self-centered or dramatic', 'Being successful', 'Shy personality', 'Reading novels a lot', 'A', 30, 'main_character_syndrome.png', 'English: \"Main character syndrome\" means thinking everything is about you.\nIndo: \"Main character syndrome\" artinya merasa seperti tokoh utama berlebihan dan narsis.'),
(178, 'slang', 18, 'What does \"That ain’t it\" mean in slang?', 'Not the right thing or choice', 'Perfect answer', 'Exciting news', 'Unbelievable', 'A', 30, 'that_aint_it.png', 'English: \"That ain’t it\" means something is wrong or doesn’t work.\nIndo: \"That ain’t it\" artinya itu bukan solusi atau pilihan yang tepat.'),
(179, 'slang', 18, 'What does \"Can’t relate\" mean in slang?', 'Not experiencing or understanding it', 'Agree completely', 'Want to join', 'Feeling curious', 'A', 30, 'cant_relate.png', 'English: \"Can’t relate\" means not able to connect or understand.\nIndo: \"Can’t relate\" artinya tidak nyambung atau tidak bisa merasakan hal yang sama.'),
(180, 'slang', 18, 'What does \"Go off\" mean in slang?', 'Keep going with passion', 'Run away', 'Get angry', 'Turn off something', 'A', 30, 'go_off.png', 'English: \"Go off\" means to keep doing something with confidence or energy.\nIndo: \"Go off\" artinya teruskan semangat atau tampil luar biasa.'),
(181, 'slang', 19, 'What does \"Crushin’ it\" mean in slang?', 'Doing really well or succeeding', 'Breaking something', 'Feeling down', 'Being rejected', 'A', 30, 'crushin_it.png', 'English: \"Crushin’ it\" means performing really well or achieving success.\nIndo: \"Crushin’ it\" artinya sukses besar atau melakukan sesuatu dengan sangat baik.'),
(182, 'slang', 19, 'What does \"The audacity\" mean in slang?', 'Shocking boldness or nerve', 'Respect', 'Kind gesture', 'Confusion', 'A', 30, 'the_audacity.png', 'English: \"The audacity\" expresses surprise at someone’s boldness.\nIndo: \"The audacity\" artinya betapa beraninya seseorang, biasanya untuk hal negatif.'),
(183, 'slang', 19, 'What does \"Unalive\" mean in slang?', 'A soft way to say die', 'To disconnect WiFi', 'To sleep deeply', 'To disappear online', 'A', 30, 'unalive.png', 'English: \"Unalive\" is a softer term for dying.\nIndo: \"Unalive\" adalah cara halus untuk mengatakan meninggal.'),
(184, 'slang', 19, 'What does \"Snack attack\" mean in slang?', 'Sudden craving to eat snacks', 'Food fight', 'Midnight meal', 'Allergic reaction', 'A', 30, 'snack_attack.png', 'English: \"Snack attack\" means a sudden urge to eat snacks.\nIndo: \"Snack attack\" artinya keinginan mendadak untuk ngemil.'),
(185, 'slang', 19, 'What does \"Don’t @ me\" mean in slang?', 'Don’t argue or reply to my opinion', 'Tag me in', 'Email me later', 'Don’t ask that', 'A', 30, 'dont_at_me.png', 'English: \"Don’t @ me\" means I said what I said—don’t try to argue.\nIndo: \"Don’t @ me\" artinya jangan bantah atau debat pendapatku.'),
(186, 'slang', 19, 'What does \"Chillax\" mean in slang?', 'To chill and relax', 'To overthink', 'To leave early', 'To eat quickly', 'A', 30, 'chillax.png', 'English: \"Chillax\" is a blend of \"chill\" and \"relax\".\nIndo: \"Chillax\" artinya bersantai sepenuhnya, santai banget.'),
(187, 'slang', 19, 'What does \"Busted\" mean in slang?', 'Looking bad or got caught', 'Very expensive', 'Fast moving', 'Stylish', 'A', 30, 'busted.png', 'English: \"Busted\" can mean someone looks bad or was caught.\nIndo: \"Busted\" artinya terlihat jelek atau ketahuan melakukan sesuatu.'),
(188, 'slang', 19, 'What does \"Pop off\" mean in slang?', 'Stand out or perform excellently', 'Explode', 'Complain loudly', 'Fall asleep suddenly', 'A', 30, 'pop_off.png', 'English: \"Pop off\" means to perform impressively or boldly.\nIndo: \"Pop off\" artinya tampil maksimal atau luar biasa.'),
(189, 'slang', 19, 'What does \"Shady\" mean in slang?', 'Suspicious or rude', 'Very bright', 'Positive', 'Funny', 'A', 30, 'shady.png', 'English: \"Shady\" means being sneaky or indirectly rude.\nIndo: \"Shady\" artinya mencurigakan atau menyindir secara halus.'),
(190, 'slang', 19, 'What does \"Wig flew\" mean in slang?', 'Shocked or amazed', 'Strong wind', 'Bad hair day', 'Running fast', 'A', 30, 'wig_flew.png', 'English: \"Wig flew\" means being extremely surprised or impressed.\nIndo: \"Wig flew\" artinya sangat kaget atau terkesan sampai seolah rambut palsu terbang.'),
(191, 'slang', 20, 'What does \"It’s giving\" mean in slang?', 'It reminds me of something or gives off a vibe', 'It’s donating', 'It’s ending', 'It’s sad', 'A', 30, 'its_giving.png', 'English: \"It’s giving\" means it reminds or represents a specific vibe or quality.\nIndo: \"It’s giving\" artinya memberi kesan atau nuansa tertentu, biasanya dipakai untuk gaya atau penampilan.');
