(193, 'slang', 20, 'What does \"Ratioed\" mean in slang?', 'More replies than likes (usually negative)', 'Balanced post', 'Exact match', 'Popular opinion', 'A', 30, 'ratioed.png', 'English: \"Ratioed\" means a post has more replies than likes—usually bad.\nIndo: \"Ratioed\" artinya lebih banyak balasan dibanding likes, sering jadi tanda post tidak disukai.'),
(194, 'slang', 20, 'What does \"Mid\" mean in slang?', 'Mediocre or average (not great)', 'Middle of the screen', 'Midnight', 'Very good', 'A', 30, 'mid.png', 'English: \"Mid\" means something is just okay or average.\nIndo: \"Mid\" artinya biasa saja atau tidak terlalu bagus.'),
