(196, 'slang', 20, 'What does \"Beige flag\" mean in slang?', 'A sign that someone is boring but not toxic', 'Big warning', 'Relationship goal', 'Amazing trait', 'A', 30, 'beige_flag.png', 'English: \"Beige flag\" is a mild warning—something odd but harmless.\nIndo: \"Beige flag\" artinya tanda bahwa seseorang agak aneh tapi tidak berbahaya.'),
(197, 'slang', 20, 'What does \"Main character energy\" mean?', 'Confidence like the star of the story', 'Being the villain', 'Stage fright', 'Getting ignored', 'A', 30, 'main_character_energy.png', 'English: \"Main character energy\" means acting with strong confidence and presence.\nIndo: \"Main character energy\" artinya punya kepercayaan diri seperti tokoh utama dalam cerita.'),
(198, 'slang', 20, 'What does \"Canon event\" mean in slang?', 'Life event that shapes someone', 'Comic book scene', 'Fashion trend', 'Deleted memory', 'A', 30, 'canon_event.png', 'English: \"Canon event\" means an unavoidable life-changing moment.\nIndo: \"Canon event\" artinya peristiwa penting yang membentuk kehidupan seseorang.'),
